Package: lint
Title: Tools to check R code style
Version: 0.3
Date: 2013-01-23
Author: Andrew Redd <andrew.redd@hsc.utah.edu>
Maintainer: Andrew Redd <andrew.redd@hsc.utah.edu>
Description: Tools for checking R code for style compliance.
    Tools for creating style compliance tests.
    A suite of pre-built tests is provided.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Imports:
